  "description": "A young boy with blonde hair is crouched down amidst a field of wildflowers and lush green grass. He is wearing an orange long-sleeved shirt with a graphic print and tan pants. He appears to be examining a flower carefully. The field extends towards a light beige dirt path, beyond which lies a body of water and a hazy, distant landmass or mountains. The vegetation is varied, with tall grasses and clusters of white and yellow wildflowers. The sky is overcast, creating soft, diffused lighting.",
